OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777997460
OL,3,CFormer supply teacher charged with
OL,4,Cupskirting pupils in schools
OL,6,FA former supply teacher from Greater
OL,7,FManchester has been charged with a
OL,8,Fstring of child sex offences,
OL,9,Fincluding upskirting and voyeurism
OL,11,FAbusali Rahman, from Salford is a
OL,12,FBritish national of Bangladeshi
OL,13,Fethnicity, and has been remanded in
OL,14,Fcustody to appear at Bolton Crown
OL,15,FCourt on Thursday 28 May.
OL,17,FThe 36 year old is charged with 12
OL,18,Fcounts of taking an indecent
OL,19,Fphotograph/pseudo-photograph of a
OL,20,Fchild, related to images allegedly
OL,21,Fobtained by upskirting.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
