OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777997460
OL,3,CFormer supply teacher charged with
OL,4,Cupskirting pupils in schools
OL,6,FHe has also been charged with three
OL,7,Fcounts of publishing an obscene
OL,8,Farticle, relating to alleged AI-
OL,9,Fgenerated sexualised images, plus
OL,10,Fthree counts of making indecent
OL,11,Fphotograph/ pseudo-photograph of a
OL,12,Fchild, relating to the alleged making
OL,13,Fof AI-generated images.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
