FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777997460
OL,3,CFormer supply teacher charged with
OL,4,Cupskirting pupils in schools
OL,6,FThe offences are alleged to have taken
OL,7,Fplace at seven high schools in Bury,
OL,8,FBolton and Salford. Police say all
OL,9,Faffected schools and the parents of 13
OL,10,Fidentified girls have been informed.
OL,11,FFour girls from two high schools have
OL,12,Fstill not been identified. GMP said
OL,13,Fthey are continuing to work those
OL,14,Fschools to identify the girls.
OL,16,FGreater Manchester Police says the
OL,17,Falleged offences took place between
OL,18,FDecember 2023 and June 2025.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
