OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777997460
OL,3,CFormer supply teacher charged with
OL,4,Cupskirting pupils in schools
OL,6,FDetective Chief Superintendent Rebecca
OL,7,FMcKendrick, head of GMP's Public
OL,8,FProtection Division, said: "I must
OL,9,Fstart by stressing that the parents of
OL,10,Fthe girls identified, and their
OL,11,Fschools, are being kept informed and
OL,12,Fsupported throughout this process.
OL,14,F"If you were not aware of this case
OL,15,Fprior to today, then your child has
OL,16,Fnot been identified as an alleged
OL,17,Fvictim.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777997460
OL,3,CFormer supply teacher charged with
OL,4,Cupskirting pupils in schools
OL,6,F"We have been in contact with all
OL,7,Fschools we know Mr Rahman worked at in
OL,8,Fthe North West since he became a
OL,9,Fqualified teacher in July 2023.
OL,11,F"No further alleged criminal offences
OL,12,Fhave been identified at this time. The
OL,13,Fpolice, schools, the local
OL,14,Fauthorities, safeguarding leads and
OL,15,Fspecialist support services are
OL,16,Fworking closely together throughout
OL,17,Fthis investigation.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777997460
OL,3,CFormer supply teacher charged with
OL,4,Cupskirting pupils in schools
OL,6,F"I understand the concern and upset
OL,7,Fthat will come with this news. It is
OL,8,Fso important that everyone refrains
OL,9,Ffrom speculation as this is an active
OL,10,Fcase where the girls affected have a
OL,11,Fright to lifelong anonymity and the
OL,12,Fdefendant has a right to a fair trial.
OL,14,F"The last thing that needed now is
OL,15,Fspeculation around this case - if you
OL,16,Fknow something, please report it
OL,17,Fdirectly to us."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
